snippet.title: SJ-19 Learns to Love! Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1441670/SJ19_Learns_To_Love

press kit: https://grizzlywizard.com/press/sj19/

SJ-19 Learns to Love is a short metroidvania about a killer robot who learns to love~ 💕 Explore, defeat bosses, and gain the power of LOVE! 

Coming May 2021!
